<body>

    <nav>
        <a href="@Url.Action("Index", "Home")">Home</a>
        <a href="@Url.Action("About", "Home")">About</a>
        <a href="@Url.Action("Services", "Home")">Services</a>
        <a href="@Url.Action("Contact", "Home")">Contact</a>
    </nav>

    <div class="container">
        <h2>About Us</h2>
        <p>We are a company focused on providing top-notch services to our clients. Our team of experts ensures high quality and satisfaction in every project.</p>
    </div>

